    "I will now consider how AI can make operators feel even more responsible -particularly when things go wrong.",
    "Moral injury refers to the psychological effect on soldiers who feel ethically compromised through their professional conduct in warfare.",
    "Human-AI teams change the decision-making environment and will change the risk calculus of moral injury.",
    "This chapter takes as a premise that militaries ought to reduce the conditions of moral injury.",
    "This premise is controversial."
